# .gitignore file created for free with Tower (https://www.git-tower.com/)
# For suggestions or improvements please contact us using support@git-tower.com
# Generated on 2025-04-23
# Includes: go, vscode, windows

### Universal ###
# Common files that should be ignored in all projects

# Logs
*.log
# Temporary files
*.tmp
*~

*.bak
# Environment files (containing secrets, API keys, credentials)
.env
*.env
.env.*

# Local configuration that shouldn't be shared
*.local

### Go ###
# go specific files

*.exe
*.test
vendor/
*.out
go.work

go.sum

### Vscode ###
# Visual Studio Code editor settings and workspace files

# Visual Studio Code
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json

!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/*.code-snippets
.history/
*.vsix
.ionide

.vs/
*.code-workspace
.vscode-test
.vscodeignore
.vscode/chrome

.vscode-server/
.vscode/sftp.json
.vscode/tags
.devcontainer/

### Windows ###
# Windows operating system specific files

Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
*.stackdump

[Dd]esktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.cab
*.msi
*.msix

*.msm
*.msp
*.lnk
*.tmp
*.bak

System Volume Information/
[Tt]emp/
$Recycle.Bin/
~$*
*.log

hiberfil.sys
pagefile.sys
*.db
Desktop.ini
ntuser.dat*
